# Centralized Analytics Components

All Recharts wrappers and chart-config code live under one folder (features/analytics/charts/)—reuse, theme consistency.

## Path Pattern
frontend/src/features/analytics/**/*.tsx

## Implementation Guidelines
- Create reusable chart components under features/analytics/charts/
- Standardize chart themes, colors, and styling
- Create wrapper components for each chart type (BarChart, LineChart, etc.)
- Keep chart configuration separate from data fetching logic
- Implement responsive design for all chart components

## Example Structure
```
frontend/src/features/analytics/
  ├── charts/
  │   ├── BarChart.tsx
  │   ├── LineChart.tsx
  │   ├── PieChart.tsx
  │   ├── AreaChart.tsx
  ├── config/
  │   ├── chartTheme.ts
  │   ├── colorPalette.ts
  ├── hooks/
  │   ├── useChartData.ts
  ├── utils/
  │   ├── dataTransformers.ts
```

## Example Implementation
```tsx
// frontend/src/features/analytics/charts/BarChart.tsx
import { BarChart as RechartsBarChart, Bar, XAxis, YAxis, Tooltip } from 'recharts';
import { chartTheme } from '../config/chartTheme';

interface BarChartProps {
  data: Array<{ name: string; value: number }>;
  height?: number;
  width?: number;
}

export const BarChart = ({ data, height = 300, width = 500 }: BarChartProps) => {
  return (
    <RechartsBarChart width={width} height={height} data={data}>
      <XAxis dataKey="name" />
      <YAxis />
      <Tooltip />
      <Bar dataKey="value" fill={chartTheme.primary} />
    </RechartsBarChart>
  );
};
```
